            <h2 class="h2">Our vision and values <span class="ec ec-rocket"></span></h2>
            <p class="p">Sexpression:UK aims for a society in which young people are able to access reliable
                information about relationships, sex and sexuality; where youth are free from STIs, and unwanted
                pregnancy; and where they are empowered to make individual, informed decisions regarding their
                bodies and their health.</p>
